sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Browser as 浏览器
    participant Controller as BookController
    participant Service as BookService
    participant Repository as BookRepository

    User->>Browser: 在搜索框输入关键词
    Browser->>Controller: 发送搜索请求 (GET /books?keyword=xxx)
    Controller->>Service: 调用 searchBooks(keyword)
    Service->>Repository: 调用 searchBooks(keyword)
    Repository-->>Service: 返回搜索结果
    Service-->>Controller: 返回图书列表
    Controller->>Service: 获取所有分类
    Service->>Repository: 查询所有分类
    Repository-->>Service: 返回分类列表
    Service-->>Controller: 返回分类列表
    Controller-->>Browser: 返回图书列表页面
    Browser-->>User: 显示搜索结果
